{"tid":1411768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩推到俾612入仁濟嗰位手足見到","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:00:31.000Z","uid":284857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d90adea5e6b909845f81ea624a4cca0b0ed5bc","tid":1411768,"uid":284857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"代朋友po, 朋友係港安做<br />\n<br />\n//早前有手足係6月12入黎求診，之後佢去到仁濟俾差佬捉左。因為差佬黎左港安問嗰位手足既個人資料，同事就話俾差佬聽嗰個人既名，性別，同埋之後會去邊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190621/s00001/1561074046227/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%AD%89%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%96%916-12%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%A7%8D%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%89-%E6%87%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561074046227%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%2589%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%2596%25916-12%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AE%2589-%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEOF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=5eb29903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561074046227%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%2589%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%2596%25916-12%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AE%2589-%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582&h=7cee2cba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190621/s00001/1561074046227/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%AD%89%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%96%916-12%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%A7%8D%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%89-%E6%87%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82</a><br />\n<br />\n係度想講既係，嗰位手足係可以去個人資料私隱專員公署投訴醫院。根據個人資料(私隱)條例第八部分第58條，個人資料保密可以係涉及罪行既情況下豁免。<br />\n<br />\n58.罪行等(1)為 &mdash;&mdash;(a)罪行的防止或偵測；<br />\n(b)犯罪者的拘捕、檢控或拘留；<br />\n(d)任何人所作的不合法或嚴重不當的行為、或不誠實的行為或舞弊行為的防止、排除或糾正(包括懲處)；<br />\ne)防止或排除因 &mdash;(ii)任何人所作的不合法或嚴重不當的行為、或不誠實的行為或舞弊行為<br />\n<br />\n但係根據當時情況，完全唔能夠推斷嗰位手足既個案有刑事成分。佢既情況冇涉及以上任何一條既條例，而當時同事提供既資料（姓名，性別，之後會去既地點），係令差佬能夠之後搵到嗰位手足。<br />\n<br />\n58.罪行等(g)本段憑藉第(3)款而適用的職能的執行，(ii)該等條文適用於該資料便相當可能會直接或間接識辨屬該資料來源的人的身分。(由2012年第18號第2條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n64.披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料屬罪行<br />\n2)如 &mdash;&mdash;(a)任何人披露未經資料使用者同意而取自該資料使用者的某資料當事人的任何個人資料；而(b)該項披露導致該當事人蒙受心理傷害，該人即屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n所以嗰位手足如果覺得令到你蒙受心理傷害既話，可以係個人資料私隱專員公署投訴醫院。<a href=\"https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/complaints/how_complaint/complaint/complaint.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcpd.org.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomplaints%2Fhow_complaint%2Fcomplaint%2Fcomplaint.html&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEOF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=2ce27452\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/complaints/how_complaint/complaint/complaint.html</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家推到俾嗰位手足見到。//<br />\n<br />\nReferences<br />\n《個人資料（私隱）條例》<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap486!en-zh-Hant-HK.pdf?FROMCAPINDEX=Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap486%21en-zh-Hant-HK.pdf%3FFROMCAPINDEX%3DY&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEOF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=d2b83fee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap486!en-zh-Hant-HK.pdf?FROMCAPINDEX=Y</a><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】證通報疑6‧12衝突槍傷者 荃灣港安：應警方要求 (07:54) - 明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190621/s00001/1561074046227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561074046227&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEOF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=ae7ab8bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561074046227&h=3c82a167\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190621/s00001/1561074046227</a>"},{"pid":"c0e5a2b1190bf291eade0d985cbcba0a57eb6aef","tid":1411768,"uid":258465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a48334eab56b1a3c35281422cd46a4bdd205ae05","tid":1411768,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1dc68526c981852800ea858fd67cc223fce55f55","tid":1411768,"uid":50043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2c954334d4a6aa20c1f1c3290686286dd3aed89","tid":1411768,"uid":40472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"推到比手足見到"}]}